<description><![CDATA[<h3>What's new in 11.0.4</h3>
<p><strong>Improved bug reporting</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Saved file names are now clearly shown</li>
<li>New "Show in Finder" buttons make the files easy to find</li>
<li>Cleaner instructions for getting reports to me</li>
<li>Window now displays correctly in dark mode</li>
</ul>
<p><strong>Behind the scenes</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Diagnostic reports now include more details, making bugs easier to fix</li>
</ul>]]></description>
